  "chapters": [
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch1",
      "text": "Whoa, the stars are insane out here. Where are we, Bob?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch2",
      "text": "Edge of the Orion Arm, Alex. Our ship’s nav system just glitched.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch3",
      "text": "Great, so we’re lost? Any ideas?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch4",
      "text": "I’d say scan for a signal. Could be a station nearby.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch5",
      "text": "Alright, let’s try that. Fingers crossed.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch6",
      "text": "Scanning now. Hope we don’t pick up pirates instead.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch7",
      "text": "Pirates? You’re joking, right?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch8",
      "text": "Out here? Not really. Signal’s coming in—looks promising.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch9",
      "text": "Okay, I’m trusting you on this. What’s it say?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch10",
      "text": "It’s a faint beacon. Could be a way out—or trouble.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch11",
      "text": "Guess we’ll find out soon. Ready?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch12",
      "text": "Born ready. Let’s chase that signal.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch13",
      "text": "Here we go then. Hold on tight!",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch14",
      "text": "Engaging thrusters now. Signal’s getting stronger.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch15",
      "text": "This better not be a wild goose chase.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch16",
      "text": "Trust me, Alex. I’ve got a good feeling about this.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch17",
      "text": "Your good feelings worry me sometimes.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch18",
      "text": "Hey, they’ve kept us alive so far, haven’t they?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch19",
      "text": "Fair point. How close are we now?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch20",
      "text": "Close enough to see something on the scanner. It’s big.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch21",
      "text": "Big like a station, or big like trouble?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch22",
      "text": "Could be both. Readings are off the charts.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch23",
      "text": "Fantastic. Any chance it’s friendly?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Alex",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png"
      },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch24",
      "text": "Maybe. It’s broadcasting a welcome signal—sort of.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": {
        "name": "Bob",
        "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png"
      },
      "isUser": false
